The version of the lead section of this page that you want does not contain the date of birth of the person after stating the name and surname and pronouncing them in the Croatian language, and this is something that is very important. Please stop vandalizing. The pages of other presidents like Donald Trump, the Portuguese president, etc. have no shorter lead section. Apart from the above, the version you are "representing" is quite gramatically incorrect.

(Only cabinets are customarily numbered in Croatia. And if any form of numbering is used at all in referencing a PM it is also far more common to use the order of their cabinet(s). E.g. Milanović would be the ''President of the 12th government''.
